E[E(X\mid Y)|Y]=E(X\mid Y)
\begin{align*}E[E(X\mid Y)|Y=y]&=\int_{-\infty}^\infty E(X\mid Y=y)f_{X\mid Y}(x\mid y)~dx\\ &=E(X\mid Y=y)\int_{-\infty}^\infty f_{X\mid Y}(x\mid y)~dx \\&=E(X\mid Y=y)\end{align*}
\text{Hence, } E[E(X\mid Y)|Y]=E(X\mid Y)
