 E(E(X|Y)|Y=y)=\int_{-\infty}^\infty E(X|Y=y)f_{X|Y=y}(x)dx=\int_{-\infty}^\infty\left(\int_{-\infty}^\infty x f_{X|Y=y}(x)dx\right)f_{X|Y=y}(x)dx\\ =\left(\int_{-\infty}^\infty x f_{X|Y=y}(x)dx\right)\int_{-\infty}^\infty f_{X|Y=y}(x)dx\\ =\left(\int_{-\infty}^\infty x f_{X|Y=y}(x)dx\right)\\ =E(X|Y) 
